{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-042__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-042", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-042__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 42.1", "sort_key": "042.001", "text_original": "道生一，一生二，二生三，三生萬物。萬物負陰而抱陽，沖氣以為和。人之所惡，唯孤﹑寡﹑不穀，而王公以為稱。故物或損之而益，或益之而損。", "text_normalized": "道生一，一生二，二生三，三生萬物。萬物負陰而抱陽，沖氣以為和。人之所惡，唯孤﹑寡﹑不穀，而王公以為稱。故物或損之而益，或益之而損。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-042__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-042", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-042__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 42.2", "sort_key": "042.002", "text_original": "人之所教，我亦教之。", "text_normalized": "人之所教，我亦教之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-042__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-003", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-042", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-042__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "老子 42.3", "sort_key": "042.003", "text_original": "強梁者不得其死，吾將以為教父。", "text_normalized": "強梁者不得其死，吾將以為教父。", "notes": ""}
